
      			CS390 PYTHON

      Startup sources for your MyLink App using SQLLITE

1. Install apache as indicated in the handout.

2. Install in your home directory in data

  cd
  tar -xvf MyLink.tar

3. Create data base

 cdMyLink 
 ./CreateDatabase.py
 ./populate.py
 ./query.py

2. To install cgi

 cd ~/apache/htdocs
 ln -s ~/MyLink/cgi MyLink
 ls PeteTwitt

3. In cgi/login.cgi look for the line MYLOGIN and write your login.

4. To run PeteTwitt app type this in a browser.

http://data.cs.purdue.edu:<port>/MyLink/login.cgi

